{"tid":2372390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勞福局局長羅致光：增5天法定假一定唔洗8年咁耐 ⋯⋯最多7年零十個月","createTime":"2021-01-19T15:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T16:39:20.000Z","uid":22556,"like":9,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e3aac72ed15deb2b61e6f437903f50edcc2989f7","tid":2372390,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T15:09:45.000Z","msg":"勞工界爭取劃一法定假期10多年，現屆政府曾表明不會處理，直至特首林鄭月娥民望跌至低點，才於去年初公佈的十大民生措施中，提出逐步增加法定假期。惟勞工顧問委員會只開會討論兩次，勞資雙方未有共識，政府便一錘定音由2022年起花8年時間將法定假期增至17天。<br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局局長羅致光表明，不會再交由勞顧會討論，並笑謂毋須8年時間完成，只需7年10個月，「不過我哋唔計得咁多啦」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210119/EBCEZBUVBVGLVLIQIMNPRPRFPE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3seuGD6c2fDBD9WuBW_vrtvNFEr1apOqgi3YTA9YOrV-zYDlF46_i4TvA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210119%2FEBCEZBUVBVGLVLIQIMNPRPRFPE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3seuGD6c2fDBD9WuBW_vrtvNFEr1apOqgi3YTA9YOrV-zYDlF46_i4TvA&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmevS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=d2bafc3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210119%2FEBCEZBUVBVGLVLIQIMNPRPRFPE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3seuGD6c2fDBD9WuBW_vrtvNFEr1apOqgi3YTA9YOrV-zYDlF46_i4TvA&h=62325005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210119/EBCEZBUVBVGLVLIQIMNPRPRFPE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3seuGD6c2fDBD9WuBW_vrtvNFEr1apOqgi3YTA9YOrV-zYDlF46_i4TvA</a>"},{"pid":"59bef2682b9a3d29e20a2f1437d24eea1b5beb9f","tid":2372390,"uid":34577,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e3aa